{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Task: Architect a high-end "Bridal Commission Application" section at the bottom of the Bespoke Bridal page.
    
    I. Typography & Aesthetic Requirements:
    
        Font Matching: All form headers and labels must match the Nancy Vuu Typography (utilizing the serif and sans-serif pairings currently active on nancyvuu.com).
    
        Styling: Use a minimalist, "Quiet Luxury" aesthetic. High white space, thin borders (0.5px or 1px), and a neutral palette. No aggressive colors; use soft blacks, whites, or muted greys for the input fields.
    
        Button Design: The "Initiate My Commission" button should be a clean, rectangular outline or solid block that matches the primary CTA buttons used in the hero sections of the site.
    
    II. Form Content & Architecture:
    
    Form Title (H2): The Bridal Commission Application
    Form Description: Our bespoke process is a sacred collaboration. Due to the master-tailored nature of our Vietnam artisans, we only accept 4 legacy commissions per month.
    
    Fields to Include:
    
        Full Name (Text)
    
        Email Address (Email)
    
        Wedding or Event Date (Date Picker)
    
        Venue or Geographic Location (Text - For Estate Visitation planning)
    
        Desired Experience Level (Radio Buttons):
    
            The Couture Commission: Precision design and architectural creation of your gown.
    
            The Bridal Immersion & Crowning: A sacred journey of identity restoration and elevation. (Recommended for the Legacy Bride).
    
        Planned Investment Level for your Gown Architecture (Dropdown):
    
            Signature Atelier ($2,500 - $6,500)
    
            Custom Bespoke ($8,500 - $15,000)
    
            Grand Legacy ($15,000+)
    
        Consultation Preference (Radio Buttons):
    
            Private San Jose Sanctuary
    
            In-Residence Estate Visitation (Atherton, Woodside, Los Altos Hills, etc.)
    
        The Power Couple Sync (Checkbox):
    
            "I am interested in harmonized bespoke suiting for my partner to complement my gown."
    
        The Vision (Long Text):
    
            Placeholder: Describe the legacy, feeling, or architectural details you wish to embody on your sacred walk.
    
    Submit Button Text: Initiate My Commission
    Success Message: Your vision has been received into our sanctuary. Nancy and the team are reviewing your architectural requirements; expect a personal invitation shortly. give me control access to edit all the content, padding, and spacing between letters and lines, Task: Re-architect the "Bridal Commission Application" at the bottom of the Bespoke Bridal page. Merge the visual elements of the previous form with the new strategic fields.
    
    I. Visual & Branding Alignment:
    
        Header Section: Center the following text at the top of the form:
    
            "Nancy Vuu Atelier Flagship | 1520 Southwest Expy #10, San Jose, CA 95126" (Small, elegant serif font).
    
            "Concierge: 1-800-401-2032" (Same styling).
    
        Typography: Use the Inherit from Theme setting to ensure fonts match the current Nancy Vuu site headers and body text.
    
        Field Style: Use Minimalist Line Borders (bottom-border only) rather than enclosed boxes to maintain an airy, high-fashion editorial feel.
    
        Spacing: Increase padding between fields to ensure a "Quiet Luxury" aesthetic.
    
    II. Form Content & Architecture:
    
    Form Title (H2): The Bridal Commission Application
    Form Description: Our bespoke process is a sacred collaboration. Due to the master-tailored nature of our Vietnam artisans, we only accept 4 legacy commissions per month.
    
    Fields to Include:
    
        Full Name (Text)
    
        Email Address (Email)
    
        Wedding or Event Date (Date Picker)
    
        Venue or Geographic Location (Text — Used for Estate Visitation planning)
    
        Desired Experience Level (Radio Buttons):
    
            The Couture Commission: The architectural design and creation of your bespoke gown.
    
            The Bridal Immersion: A comprehensive journey of identity restoration and elevation, culminating in the creation of your master-tailored bespoke gown.
    
        Planned Investment Level for Gown Architecture (Dropdown):
    
            Signature Atelier ($2,500 - $6,500)
    
            Custom Bespoke ($8,500 - $15,000)
    
            Grand Legacy ($15,000+)
    
        Consultation Preference (Radio Buttons):
    
            Private San Jose Sanctuary
    
            In-Residence Estate Visitation (Atherton, Woodside, Los Altos Hills, etc.)
    
        The Power Couple Sync (Checkbox):
    
            "I am interested in harmonized bespoke suiting for my partner to complement my gown."
    
        The Vision (Long Text Area):
    
            Placeholder Text: Tell us about yourself and the legacy or architectural details you wish to embody on your sacred walk.
    
    Submit Button Text: Initiate My Commission
    Success Message: Your vision has been received into our sanctuary. Nancy and the team are reviewing your architectural requirements; expect a personal invitation shortly.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-bridal-commission-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.form_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__top-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.top_info_margin_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__address-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-bridal-commission__phone-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font.weight }};
    font-style: {{ block.settings.heading_font.style }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.top_info_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.top_info_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.top_info_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.top_info_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.top_info_line_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__phone-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_margin_bottom }}px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font.weight }};
    font-style: {{ block.settings.heading_font.style }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.title_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.title_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_margin_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.body_font.weight }};
    font-style: {{ block.settings.body_font.style }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.description_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.description_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__form-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.form_margin_top }}px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.field_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.label_font_weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.label_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.label_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.label_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.label_color }};
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.label_margin_bottom }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.label_text_transform }};
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__input-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-bridal-commission__select-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-bridal-commission__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.input_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.input_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.input_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.input_text_color }};
    background-color: {{ block.settings.input_background_color }};
    border: 0;
    border-bottom: {{ block.settings.input_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.input_border_color }};
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: {{ block.settings.input_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.input_padding_horizontal }}px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus,
  .ai-bridal-commission__select-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus,
  .ai-bridal-commission__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-bottom-color: {{ block.settings.input_focus_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    min-height: {{ block.settings.textarea_min_height }}px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-bridal-commission__checkbox-group-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.radio_checkbox_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-bridal-commission__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-bridal-commission__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__option-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.option_label_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.option_label_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.option_label_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.option_label_color }};
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__button-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.button_margin_top }}px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.button_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_font_weight }};
    line-height: {{ block.settings.button_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.button_letter_spacing }}em;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.button_text_transform }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text_color }};
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__success-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.success_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.success_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.success_letter_spacing }}em;
    color: {{ block.settings.success_text_color }};
    background-color: {{ block.settings.success_background_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.success_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.success_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.success_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.success_padding }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.success_margin_top }}px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-bridal-commission__error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.error_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.error_text_color }};
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-bridal-commission-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_bottom }}px;
    }

    .ai-bridal-commission__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_title_font_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-bridal-commission__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_description_font_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-bridal-commission__top-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.mobile_top_info_margin_bottom }}px;
    }

    .ai-bridal-commission__address-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-bridal-commission__phone-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_top_info_font_size }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<bridal-commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}
  class="ai-bridal-commission-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  <div class="ai-bridal-commission__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.show_top_info %}
      <div class="ai-bridal-commission__top-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.address_text != blank %}
          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__address-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.address_text }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.phone_text != blank %}
          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__phone-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.phone_text }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-bridal-commission__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.form_title != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-bridal-commission__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.form_title }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.form_description != blank %}
        <div class="ai-bridal-commission__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.form_description }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="ai-bridal-commission__form-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {%- form 'contact' -%}
        <input type="hidden" name="contact[bridal_commission]" value="true">

        {% if form.posted_successfully? %}
          <div
            class="ai-bridal-commission__success-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            id="ai-bridal-commission-success-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.success_message }}
          </div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-bridal-commission-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.label_full_name }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="ai-bridal-commission-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[name]"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              placeholder="{{ block.settings.placeholder_full_name }}"
              required
            >
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-bridal-commission-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.label_email }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="ai-bridal-commission-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[email]"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              placeholder="{{ block.settings.placeholder_email }}"
              autocomplete="email"
              {% if form.errors %}
                aria-invalid="true"
                aria-describedby="ai-bridal-commission-email-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              {% endif %}
              required
            >
            {%- if form.errors -%}
              <div
                id="ai-bridal-commission-email-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                class="ai-bridal-commission__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {{ form.errors.messages.email }}
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-bridal-commission-event-date-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.label_event_date }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="ai-bridal-commission-event-date-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[event_date]"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              placeholder="{{ block.settings.placeholder_event_date }}"
            >
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-bridal-commission-location-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.label_location }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="ai-bridal-commission-location-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[location]"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              placeholder="{{ block.settings.placeholder_location }}"
            >
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.label_experience_level }}
            </label>
            <div class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="radio"
                  id="ai-bridal-commission-experience-couture-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[experience_level]"
                  value="{{ block.settings.option_experience_couture }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-bridal-commission-experience-couture-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__option-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.option_experience_couture }}
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="radio"
                  id="ai-bridal-commission-experience-immersion-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[experience_level]"
                  value="{{ block.settings.option_experience_immersion }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-bridal-commission-experience-immersion-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__option-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.option_experience_immersion }}
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-bridal-commission-investment-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.label_investment }}
            </label>
            <select
              id="ai-bridal-commission-investment-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[investment_level]"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__select-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              <option value="">{{ block.settings.investment_placeholder }}</option>
              <option value="{{ block.settings.option_investment_signature }}">{{ block.settings.option_investment_signature }}</option>
              <option value="{{ block.settings.option_investment_bespoke }}">{{ block.settings.option_investment_bespoke }}</option>
              <option value="{{ block.settings.option_investment_legacy }}">{{ block.settings.option_investment_legacy }}</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.label_consultation }}
            </label>
            <div class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="radio"
                  id="ai-bridal-commission-consultation-sanctuary-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[consultation_preference]"
                  value="{{ block.settings.option_consultation_sanctuary }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-bridal-commission-consultation-sanctuary-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__option-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.option_consultation_sanctuary }}
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="radio"
                  id="ai-bridal-commission-consultation-estate-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[consultation_preference]"
                  value="{{ block.settings.option_consultation_estate }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-bridal-commission-consultation-estate-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__option-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.option_consultation_estate }}
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-bridal-commission__checkbox-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-bridal-commission__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
                  id="ai-bridal-commission-couple-sync-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[couple_sync]"
                  value="yes"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-bridal-commission-couple-sync-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-bridal-commission__option-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.checkbox_couple_sync }}
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-bridal-commission-vision-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.label_vision }}
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="ai-bridal-commission-vision-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[vision]"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              placeholder="{{ block.settings.placeholder_vision }}"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="ai-bridal-commission__button-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="ai-bridal-commission__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.button_text }}
            </button>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {%- endform -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</bridal-commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class BridalCommissionForm{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        const form = this.querySelector('form');
        if (!form) return;

        const successMessage = this.querySelector('.ai-bridal-commission__success-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (successMessage) {
          successMessage.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
        }
      }
    }

